description: AMUNDI MSCI NORDIC UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI Nordic Countries Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to around 80 leading stocks on the Scandinavian market (Denmark, Finland, Norway, Sweden), with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi MSCI Nordic UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
